PROJECT BLAZE - EXPLICIT 7-ROBOT LONG INPUT TEST DATA
=====================================================

Purpose
-------
This file documents a longer demo workload for Project Blaze using 7 robots
and 42 tasks. It is intended for presentation, testing, and to match the
backend demo configuration and frontend comparison panel.

Assumptions used by this input
------------------------------
1. Worker / robot count: 7
2. Scheduling strategies compared: FIFO and Priority
3. All tasks are seeded into the scheduler at demo time t = 0 s
4. Priority strategy is non-preemptive:
	- High > Normal > Low
	- FIFO order is preserved inside the same priority band
5. Task duration is the simulated execution duration
6. The 42-task dataset is built from the base 18 tasks repeated as workload waves


