SECTION E - WHY THIS 7-ROBOT DEMO IS GOOD FOR PRESENTATION
----------------------------------------------------------
1. It uses more robots, so the robot status panel changes more often.
2. It uses a longer 42-task workload, so the dashboard has enough time to show:
	- Pending tasks
	- Running tasks
	- Finished tasks
	- Working / Idle / Stopped robot transitions
3. With 7 robots, FIFO and Priority have the same overall makespan in this dataset (47 s),
	but Priority still finishes urgent tasks far earlier.
4. That makes the scheduling tradeoff easy to explain in the demo.


